'''Trillia''' was the copilot of [[Jax Keyn]]'s [[YT-1300 light freighter/Legends|YT-1300 light freighter]], the [[Blackjack (YT-1300 light freighter)|''Blackjack'']]. She helped him rescue [[Mon Mothma/Legends|Mon Mothma]] from the clutches of [[Pel Talon]].

